Unsolicited Reviews from strangers are my favorite feedback.  From a delivery man: 

He said that when he arrived, he wasn’t sure that he was at the right place, because there was such a pleasant vibe in the lobby that reminded him of a bar or lounge. 

And that our building makes him feel like he’s walking in New York … 

He also mentioned multiple times that he would love to live in a place like this forever…

“ at a place like this - you leave to work in the morning and have a stressful day… but when you come back home… you’re like - “I work?”… and completely forget about your worries”

Meet Dorothy Macik, our October Designer Spotlight and the creative force behind LA-based Dorothy Macik Design. Dorothy brings a fresh perspective to interior design, specializing in a warm minimalism aesthetic for large-scale residential and extensive commercial projects.

I specify Zephyr ventilation for every project I design because I am an avid cook myself and experience their quality and power on a daily basis in my personal kitchen," Dorothy shared. “I have been designing kitchens for more than a decade and I am so happy to be able to specify products I am confident in. Zephyr has never disappointed!"

Follow Dorothy (@dorothymacik) for inspiration that marries style and functionality.
